but thought you would want to know!
Ronnie at www.type2parts.com is accepting donations towards a new bus.  The
sooner the better!!  We raised close to $1000 at BBB8!!  And it was very
kind of London Bridge Bullis to allow it.  They deserve a giant Thank You
